OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780902267
OL,3,CHow the Euro 96 football tournament
OL,4,Ccould hold the key to Melanie Hall's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FPolice investigating the murder of
OL,8,FMelanie Hall believe memories of the
OL,9,Fopening match of the Euro 96 football
OL,10,Ftournament could help solve the cold
OL,11,Fcase.
OL,13,FMelanie was last seen alive in the
OL,14,Fearly hours of 9 June, 1996, inside
OL,15,FCadillacs night club in Bath. She was
OL,16,Fout the night before, which was the
OL,17,Fopening match of the European Football
OL,18,FChampionship.
OL,20,FHer remains were found thirteen years
OL,21,Flater in Gloucestershire.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
