PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780902267
OL,3,CHow the Euro 96 football tournament
OL,4,Ccould hold the key to Melanie Hall's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FApproaching the 30th anniversary of
OL,8,Fher disappearance, Melanie's family
OL,9,Fremain desperate for answers.
OL,11,FDetectives at Avon and Somerset Police
OL,12,Fsay Bath would have been vibrant and
OL,13,Fbusy on the night of Melanie's
OL,14,Fdisappearance. The force has made a
OL,15,Fnew video as part of its campaign to
OL,16,Fseek justice for her family.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780902267
OL,3,CHow the Euro 96 football tournament
OL,4,Ccould hold the key to Melanie Hall's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FIt uses a clip from 'Three Lions' By
OL,8,FBaddiel, Skinner and the Lightning
OL,9,FSeeds. The performers and record label
OL,10,Fgave their permission for this to be
OL,11,Fused in the campaign.
OL,13,FThe force hopes it will jog the
OL,14,Fmemories of people who were out
OL,15,Fenjoying the opening match of the Euro
OL,16,F'96 football tournament.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
