PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780902267
OL,3,CHow the Euro 96 football tournament
OL,4,Ccould hold the key to Melanie Hall's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Ben Lavender
OL,8,Fof Avon and Somerset Police said: "The
OL,9,Fmurder of Melanie Hall is one of the
OL,10,Flongest running and highest profile
OL,11,Finvestigations ever carried out by
OL,12,FAvon and Somerset Police, with
OL,13,Fhundreds of officers working on the
OL,14,Fcase over the years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780902267
OL,3,CHow the Euro 96 football tournament
OL,4,Ccould hold the key to Melanie Hall's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"As we approach the 30th anniversary,
OL,8,Fthe 'Justice for Melanie' campaign is
OL,9,Fasking people to think back: Just a
OL,10,Fminute of your time, to take you back
OL,11,Fto Saturday, 8 June 1996. Just a
OL,12,Fnormal night out in Bath enjoying a
OL,13,Ffew drinks with your friends.
OL,15,F"Not just another night for Melanie
OL,16,FHall. It was the last confirmed
OL,17,Fsighting of her alive.
OL,19,F"Just one small detail or memory. It
OL,20,Fcould prove to be a huge breakthrough
OL,21,Fand solve Melanie's murder."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780902267
OL,3,CHow the Euro 96 football tournament
OL,4,Ccould hold the key to Melanie Hall's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"Melanie's family have endured
OL,8,Funimaginable pain and uncertainty for
OL,9,Fthree decades and have shown
OL,10,Fextraordinary strength and resilience
OL,11,Fthroughout this time.
OL,13,F"Everything we do is driven by the
OL,14,Fneed to provide them with the justice
OL,15,Fand answers they so desperately need."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
