OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780902267
OL,3,CHow the Euro 96 football tournament
OL,4,Ccould hold the key to Melanie Hall's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV News, ahead of the
OL,8,F30th anniversary of Melanie's death,
OL,9,Fher sister Dom said: "I feel very
OL,10,Fangry that she lost her life at 25,
OL,11,Fthat someone chose to take that away
OL,12,Ffrom her.
OL,14,F"I'm so angry that I lost my sister.
OL,15,FIt's like I've lost part of myself,
OL,16,Fpart of my identity. I'm also angry
OL,17,Ffor my children that they lost their
OL,18,Fauntie, who would have had a massive
OL,19,Finfluence on their young lives."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780902267
OL,3,CHow the Euro 96 football tournament
OL,4,Ccould hold the key to Melanie Hall's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FSteve Hall, Melanie's father, said,
OL,8,F"People talk about closure. But the
OL,9,Fonly closure I'd get is if Melanie
OL,10,Fwalked through that door. So there's
OL,11,Fnever going to be closure for us."
OL,13,FBut he said that if Melanie's killer
OL,14,Fwere identified it would mean "at
OL,15,Fleast we've done all we possibly can."
OL,17,FMelanie's mother, Pat, now suffers
OL,18,Ffrom advanced dementia.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780902267
OL,3,CHow the Euro 96 football tournament
OL,4,Ccould hold the key to Melanie Hall's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"She's not going to get any the
OL,8,Fanswers that she needs, or needed,"
OL,9,Fsaid Dom.
OL,11,F"So it's really down to me and dad now
OL,12,Fto speak on behalf of my mum as well.
OL,13,FEven though mum won't understand
OL,14,Fwhat's happening and she won't
OL,15,Funderstand any answers if we get them,
OL,16,Fwe'd still be doing justice for my
OL,17,Fmum."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780902267
OL,3,CHow the Euro 96 football tournament
OL,4,Ccould hold the key to Melanie Hall's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"Thirty years is a long time, isn't
OL,8,Fit? She's been gone longer than she
OL,9,Fwas alive. It's a very strange
OL,10,Fconcept," said Dom Hall, Melanie's
OL,11,Folder sister.
OL,13,F"Dad's 82 now, and I'm not far off 60,
OL,14,Fand I think, you know, time is really
OL,15,Fgoing on, and I hope we get the
OL,16,Fanswers that we need and the justice
OL,17,Ffor her."
OL,19,FSteve Hall said he hoped someone who
OL,20,Fknew the killer would finally search
OL,21,Ftheir conscience.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780902267
OL,3,CHow the Euro 96 football tournament
OL,4,Ccould hold the key to Melanie Hall's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"I think what we're hoping for is that
OL,8,Fat some point in time, there will be a
OL,9,Fchange of mind for whatever reason it
OL,10,Fmay be.
OL,12,F"Someone is is dying and they want to
OL,13,Fmake a confession. It may be that
OL,14,Fsomeone has suddenly fallen out with
OL,15,Ftheir partner and no longer wants to
OL,16,Fprotect them.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780902267
OL,3,CHow the Euro 96 football tournament
OL,4,Ccould hold the key to Melanie Hall's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"But I feel that somewhere along the
OL,8,Fline, we are hoping that there will be
OL,9,Fa change in someone's mind and that
OL,10,Fthey will come forward with
OL,11,Finformation that, for whatever reason,
OL,12,Fthey withheld until now."
OL,14,FThe Charity Crimestoppers has offered
OL,15,Fa #20,000 reward for information.
OL,17,FWhat more do we know about Melanie
OL,18,FHall's disappearance?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
