PN,43913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780902267
OL,3,CHow the Euro 96 football tournament
OL,4,Ccould hold the key to Melanie Hall's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FMelanie Hall, who was 25 and a
OL,8,Fhospital clerical worker, had been on
OL,9,Fa night out with her boyfriend, a
OL,10,Fdoctor, Phillip Karlbaum and two
OL,11,Ffriends.
OL,13,FAfter going to a barbecue, they went
OL,14,Fto Cadillacs night club where Melanie
OL,15,Fand Dr Karlbaum argued. He left the
OL,16,Fclub.
OL,18,FMelanie was last seen at 1.10am on
OL,19,FSunday 9 June sitting on a stool by
OL,20,Fthe dance floor.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780902267
OL,3,CHow the Euro 96 football tournament
OL,4,Ccould hold the key to Melanie Hall's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FHer coat was checked out of the
OL,8,Fcloakroom, so detectives believed she
OL,9,Fleft the club but she was reported
OL,10,Fmissing after she failed to return to
OL,11,Fwork on the Monday morning.
OL,13,FHer remains were found in undergrowth
OL,14,Fon a motorway verge by the northbound
OL,15,Fstretch of the M5 at Junction 14 in
OL,16,FOctober 2009.
OL,18,FA postmortem later declared she had
OL,19,Fsuffered blunt trauma to her head.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
