OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780902267
OL,3,CHow the Euro 96 football tournament
OL,4,Ccould hold the key to Melanie Hall's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FThere have been several arrests in
OL,8,Fconnection with Melanie's murder over
OL,9,Fthe year, but no-one has been charged.
OL,10,FForensic investigations have been
OL,11,Fcarried out on the black bags and the
OL,12,Frope found with Melanie's remains.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
